BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//msnbc.msn.com/id/8452611/"&gt;Japan: Eruption made 3,300-ft. vapor column&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Associated%20Press"&gt;The Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 4, 2005

</ul>


