BULLET::::- Philip Thornton. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.independent.co.uk/business/news/article296694.ece"&gt;Abbott Laborotories faced with anti-Aids drug dilemma&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AIndependent"&gt;Independent&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 4, 2005
