BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2005/WORLD/europe/07/06/g8.main/"&gt;G8 protesters clash with police&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 6, 2005

</ul>


