BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2005/SPORT/07/06/singapore.olympics/index.html"&gt;London wins 2012 Olympics&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 6, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.news24.com/News24/Sport/More_Sport/0%2C%2C2-9-32_1733041%2C00.html"&gt;London edged it by four votes&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANews24"&gt;News24&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 6, 2005
