BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.eicta.org/press.asp%3Flevel2%3D42%26amp%3Blevel1%3D6%26amp%3Blevel0%3D1%26amp%3Bdocid%3D404"&gt;Europe's High Tech Industry Welcomes European Parliament Decision&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AEICTA"&gt;EICTA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 6, 2005

