BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//today.reuters.com/news/NewsArticle.aspx%3Ftype%3DbusinessNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D2005-07-07T101230Z_01_L07682729_RTRIDST_0_BUSINESS-MARKETS-STOCKS-US-EUROPE-DC.XML"&gt;Wall St seen sharply lower&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 7, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx%3Ftype%3DbusinessNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D2005-07-07T103216Z_01_L07551279_RTRIDST_0_BUSINESS-MARKETS-EUROPE-STOCKS-DC.XML"&gt;FTSE, Europe shares tumble after blasts&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 7, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.bloomberg.com/apps/news%3Fpid%3D10000100%26amp%3Bsid%3DabEz3mu6K14E%26amp%3Brefer%3Dgermany"&gt;European Stocks Drop, Led by British Airways on London Blasts&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABloomberg"&gt;Bloomberg&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 7, 2005
