BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/L07621399.htm"&gt;France tightens security after London blasts&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 7, 2005
</ul>
 


