BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.guardian.co.uk/worldlatest/story/0%2C1280%2C-5125223%2C00.html"&gt;Romanian Cabinet to Resign After Ruling&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Guardian"&gt;The Guardian&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 7, 2005

</ul>


