BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.scotsman.com/scotland.cfm%3Fid%3D757722005"&gt;Suspicious packages bring fear to Scotland&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Scotsman"&gt;The Scotsman&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 8, 2005

</ul>


