BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.msnbc.msn.com/id/8511662/"&gt;Court agrees ‘partial birth’ law unconstitutional&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 8, 2005

</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- Kevin O'Hanlon. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/nation/wire/sns-ap-abortion-trials%2C1%2C3206073.story%3Fcoll%3Dsns-ap-nation-headlines"&gt;Neb. Court Upholds Partial Birth Decision&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 8, 2005

</ul>


