BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20050710/ap_on_re_eu/britain_birmingham_alert%3B_ylt%3DAtPfInOWB8uFP0NDVEgCoses0NUE%3B_ylu%3DX3oDMTA3b3JuZGZhBHNlYwM3MjE-"&gt;Thousands Evacuated From Birmingham Centre&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAP"&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 10, 2005

</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20050710/wl_afp/britainattacks_050710082549%3B_ylt%3DApor7VTiGZaDP9q8i4PQU26s0NUE%3B_ylu%3DX3oDMTA3b3JuZGZhBHNlYwM3MjE-"&gt;Nerves fray in Britain as hunt widens for bombers amid new scare&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAFP"&gt;AFP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 10, 2005

