BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/4670379.stm"&gt;Srebrenica Muslims bury the dead&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News"&gt;BBC News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 11, 2005

