BULLET::::- Larry Neil. "&lt;a href="http%3A//icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/0100news/0100regionalnews/tm_objectid%3D15722399%26amp%3Bmethod%3Dfull%26amp%3Bsiteid%3D50061%26amp%3Bheadline%3Dculture-capital-cash-go-ahead-name_page.html"&gt;Culture capital go-ahead&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ALiverpool%20Daily%20Post"&gt;Liverpool Daily Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 11, 2005

</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/merseyside/4672529.stm"&gt;Culture city wins £33m for museum&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC"&gt;BBC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 11, 2005

</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/3907541.stm"&gt;Fourth Grace plans 'unworkable'&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC"&gt;BBC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 19, 2004

