BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cbc.ca/news/story/2005/07/12/cuba-hurricane050712.html"&gt;Cuba raises death toll, rejects U.S. help&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACBC%20News"&gt;CBC News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 12, 2005

