BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/4679681.stm"&gt;London bombing victims remembered&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC"&gt;BBC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 14, 2005

</ul>


