<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20050714/ap_on_sc/big_bones%3B_ylt%3DAg_RQFUf3t8nAfX8xSxLgCUPLBIF%3B_ylu%3DX3oDMTBiMW04NW9mBHNlYwMlJVRPUCUl"&gt;Bones of a Mammoth possibly found in Silicon Valley&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 15, 2005

