</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.foe.co.uk/resource/press_releases/government_reveals_huge_im_14072005.html"&gt;Government reveals huge impact of food miles&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AFriends%20of%20the%20Earth"&gt;Friends of the Earth&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 15 2005

