BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//sacramento.bizjournals.com/sacramento/stories/2005/07/11/daily37.html"&gt;Supermarkets and drugstores sue Visa&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASacramento%20Business%20Journal"&gt;Sacramento Business Journal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 16, 2005
BULLET::::- Lauren Weber. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.newsday.com/business/ny-bzvisa4345525jul16%2C0%2C7869941.story%3Fcoll%3Dny-business-headlines"&gt;Retailers sue over credit card fees&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANewsday"&gt;Newsday&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 16, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.baltimoresun.com/business/bal-bz.grocers16jul16%2C1%2C848627.story%3Fcoll%3Dbal-business-headlines"&gt;Grocers, drugstore chains sue Visa over fees for transactions&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABaltimore%20Sun"&gt;Baltimore Sun&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 16, 2005 ♡❤subscription♡❤

