</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- Bob Marshall. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.fieldandstream.com/fieldstream/columnists/conservation/article/0%2C13199%2C465391%2C00.html"&gt;Ducks Out of Water?&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AField%20%26amp%3B%20Stream"&gt;Field &amp; Stream&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 18, 2005

</ul>
