BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.bloomberg.com/apps/news%3Fpid%3D10000087%26amp%3Bsid%3Da0ysHmTBryYI%26amp%3Brefer%3Dtop_world_news"&gt;Bush Plans Announcement on U.S. Supreme Court Nominee&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABloomberg"&gt;Bloomberg&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 18, 2005

</ul>


