BULLET::::- Rob Gilles. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/07/20/AR2005072001811.html"&gt;Canada 4th Nation to Legalize Gay Marriage&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 20, 2005

</ul>
