BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Associated%20Press"&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.msnbc.msn.com/id/8663402/"&gt;House votes to extend Patriot Act&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AMSNBC"&gt;MSNBC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 21, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//georgewbush-whitehouse.archives.gov/ask/20050720.html"&gt;Paul McNulty hosts 'Ask the White House'&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWhiteHouse.gov"&gt;WhiteHouse.gov&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 20, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.lifeandliberty.gov/subs/q_support.htm"&gt;Congress Speaks&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUnited%20States%20Department%20of%20Justice"&gt;United States Department of Justice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 20, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//georgewbush-whitehouse.archives.gov/news/releases/2005/07/20050720-4.html"&gt;President Encourages Renewal of Patriot Act Provisions&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWhiteHouse.gov"&gt;WhiteHouse.gov&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 20, 2005

