BULLET::::- Julian Walker. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.timesdispatch.com/servlet/Satellite%3Fpagename%3DRTD/MGArticle/RTD_BasicArticle%26amp%3Bc%3DMGArticle%26amp%3Bcid%3D1031783995900"&gt;Alleged gator killer faces charges&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ARichmond%20Times-Dispatch"&gt;Richmond Times-Dispatch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 22, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.fws.gov/endangered/i/C0O.html"&gt;American alligator&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AU.S.%20Fish%20and%20Wildlife%20Service"&gt;U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July , 2005
