BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.ilph.org/campaigns/horse_passports.asp"&gt;Under current EU legislation, all horses and ponies must have a passport&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AInternational%20League%20for%20the%20Protection%20of%20Horses"&gt;International League for the Protection of Horses&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;,

</ul>


