BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//washingtontimes.com/upi/20050722-122448-2956r.htm"&gt;Iranian teens convicted of rape executed&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashington%20Times"&gt;Washington Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 22, 2005
