BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/news%3Ftmpl%3Dstory%26amp%3Bu%3D/nm/20050723/ts_nm/security_britain_alert_dc"&gt;Alert ends at London underground station&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 23, 2005

