BULLET::::- Inter Milan. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.inter.it/aas/news/reader%3FN%3D19415%26amp%3BL%3Den"&gt;Inter cancels England tour&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AInter%20Milan"&gt;Inter Milan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 23, 2005

</ul>
